These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, whisting
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, ritmeester, montecristo, alhambra
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, quad-bike, taxi
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, canasta, chess
1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the swisher-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is whisting is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing bridge##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
9. the person who's hobby is whisting is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | whisting  | camping | card-games |
| Cigar           | ritmeester | swisher | alhambra  | montecristo  |
| Transport   | taxi       | quad-bike      | bus | snowmobile      |
| Game           | bridge          | whist     | canasta    | chess     |

