.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, aquamarine, purple, blue
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish, horse, goldfish
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, accountant, musician, manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
2. the manager is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the manager is on the left of the dancer##1
6. the person who likes purple is the musician##1
7. the accountant is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color      | purple     | mauve       | aquamarine | blue        |
| Pet          | goldfish     | fish       | horse   | guinea-pig   |
| Job   | musician      | accountant       | manager     | dancer    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

