.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, march, december
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
There 4 different types of food: spinach, raspberry, cranberry, pear
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, airplane, snowmobile, motorbike
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday      | november | june       | december        | march        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Food   | spinach     | raspberry    | pear | cranberry        |
| Transport           | snowmobile         | train  | motorbike       | airplane         |

