.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, bike, roller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, electronic, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, collecting, board-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, baseball, sailing, soccer
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person driving the car##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
9. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Transport           | car   | trike  | roller | bike |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Hobby   | collecting       | board-games    | dancing     | cooking  |
| Sport           | baseball     | sailing | soccer     | parkour         |

