.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, spinach, lettuce, avocado
House: art-deco, colonial, ranch-style, craftsman
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, oliveros, cain, prince
1. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person eating onion##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
6. the prince-smoker is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the art-deco house##1
8. the person eating spinach is on the right of the colonial house##1
9. the art-deco house is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Food           | onion  | lettuce    | spinach | avocado |
| House   | ranch-style      | colonial    | art-deco         | craftsman    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Cigar         | oliveros | davidoff | prince      | cain      |

