The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, amaryllis, begonia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, woodworking, card-games, filmmaking
 1. the person who likes emerald is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person who likes black is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who growsrose is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who likes black##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Color          | black  | lilac | emerald     | ivory |
| Flower           | amaryllis  | begonia      | rose | balloon-flower    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Hobby           | card-games   | filmmaking       | gardening       | woodworking      |

