 3. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the ranch-style house##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of house##1
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | indie | house     | blues    | funk |
| Flower       | iris | begonia    | orchid | azalea |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| House   | victorian   | farmhouse | craftsman    | ranch-style |

