The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour, skateboarding, swimming
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, western, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, salsa, country, folk
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person playing backgammon is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of soul##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is the fan of soul##1
8. the fan of country is the person playing whist##1
9. the fan of folk is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Game      | backgammon      | whist         | snooker        | poker      |
| Sport           | parkour | water-polo | skateboarding  | swimming  |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | musical     | time-travel | zombie     |
| Music-Genre     | soul        | country     | salsa     | folk |

