.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade, tea
City: venice, new-york, boston, london
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, cat, bird
There 4 different types of food: onion, tomato, artichoke, grapes
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person traveling to london##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is the person drinking tea##1
9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | tea           | juice    | lemonade    |
| City         | boston  | new-york | venice  | london |
| Pet   | cat     | fish     | hedgehog | bird   |
| Food         | grapes | onion     | tomato | artichoke     |

