4. the person eating mango is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the art-deco house is on the left of the cottage house##1
8. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | asparagus | mango     | kiwi       | raspberry |
